# Project Core Architecture

- Follow SRP strictly: one screen = one responsibility, one cubit = one feature flow.
- Keep dependency direction clean: `presentation -> domain -> data`; no reverse imports.
- Use `get_it` + `injectable` for DI only; never create repositories/services directly in widgets.
- After new/changed `@injectable` registrations, regenerate DI (`build_runner`).
- Use `cubit` for screen state; avoid business logic inside widgets.
- Cubit: state + cubit in **one file**; repository contract + **impl in one file**; models with **freezed** (+ json_serializable for API). See `dart-feature-conventions.mdc`.
- DI: `@injectable` (factory) by default; `@lazySingleton`/`@singleton` only when one shared instance is required.
- Use `auto_route` for navigation; add typed routes in router config, then regenerate route files.
- No duplicate sources of truth: keep one canonical data source per feature.
- `lib/feature_draft/` — черновики; продакшен-фичи — в `lib/feature/<name>/` (см. `dart-feature-conventions.mdc`).
- Before finishing: run analyzer on touched files and fix introduced issues.
